Bail has been granted to all seven accused suspects in the VBS looting matter. Earlier the suspects believed to be involved in the looting of funds appeared in the Specialised Commercial Crimes Court. The arrests follow early morning raids in different parts of Gauteng and Limpopo. #eNCA​ Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Bail has been granted to all seven accused suspects in the VBS looting matter. READ: VBS case postponed, more charges and arrests anticipated Earlier, the suspects believed to be involved in the looting of funds appeared in the Specialised Commercial Crimes Court. READ: Hawks arrest five people in connection with VBS looting The arrests follow raids in different parts of Gauteng and Limpopo. The group faces a combined 188 charges, including theft, fraud, corruption, money laundering and racketeering. Watch the video above for more on this story.